What you need to know:

A 60-year-old granny says she lost 17 cows  worth Sh1.8 million to security agencies from Borabu during a cattle rustling raid.The last time she visited Manga Police Station, she was "harassed by the officers".She is now  pleading with Interior CS Fred Matiang’i to tame the few rogue officers who spoil the, otherwise, good name of our security forces.